{"tid":2402450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得安心出殯係信用評分系統嘅前奏","createTime":"2021-02-10T12:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T12:44:42.000Z","uid":265840,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2232ed7dd6d8c320d4d577d32d499115d534d927","tid":2402450,"uid":265840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"google返 香港 社會信用制度 就會見到一堆19年底嘅新聞<br />\n當時個風吹行到連正苦都要跳出嚟澄清絕不會推行<br />\n但大家都知正苦越澄清得嘅就越係會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇埋哩排越嚟越多巴士卡機隔籬都加裝咗個qr code scanner<br />\n上面寫就寫係咩tng電子錢包 香港人的電子錢包<br />\n但我對tng唯一認識就係間公司涉嫌碌匯豐卡賺cash refund<br />\n身邊亦都唔見有人用緊/用過哩樣嘢<br />\n定唔知係我個圈子太井底之蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再search多兩search<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/ourhongkongfoundation/videos/697236134044719/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fourhongkongfoundation%2Fvideos%2F697236134044719%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=6e9a2032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/ourhongkongfoundation/videos/697236134044719/</a><br />\n團結香港基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟手宜家就由食肆開始強推要scan安心出殯先入得<br />\n真係好有理由相信喺不久嘅將來<br />\n哩啲所謂電子錢包嘅qr code scanner就會直接轉哂做社會信用系統嘅scanner<br />\n一個code link哂你id 屋企住邊 銀行戶口嘅錢 同埋個社會信用系統評分<br />\n到時就同支那一樣<br />\n信用低嘅莫講話搭飛機出國移民<br />\n分分鐘連你搭巴士去返工都唔得<br />\n一係有能力養車一係行路返工一係等死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dce9dd8961c0fed44e0003cb4ec20205d3e065","tid":2402450,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ad3163617ff52afd57bdaa111d06eea368deee","tid":2402450,"uid":30201,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有sim卡實名制<br />\n<br />\n前奏黎"},{"pid":"02db5b29216336c4b20539b3554eb475875d0d2e","tid":2402450,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"我可以答你：係<br />\n<br />\n堂食明顯係第一步，若果無有效抗爭，港共之後一定將狗帶碼推廣到商場、交通工具各方面<br />\n<br />\n私了狗帶碼，事在必行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2402252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2402252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6788191403c06339c620cce25d8912ed99cfebd5","tid":2402450,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}